name: Incestor
description:
This is a joke game made by Ahmed Khalifa and Aphrodite Andreou for the Global Game Jam 2023 with the theme of Roots. The game is made in Flicksy 2 by Mark Wonnacott. Please support them and hope the tool grows and be more stable. Thanks a lot for creating Flicksy 2.

In Incestor, you try to incest with your ancestors by traveling back in time. This is a joke game so please don't take it too seriously and have fun.

Use the mouse to click on anything in the game.
